The paper deals with facial expression recognition using deep neural networks, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep neural networks also suggests that the paper may fall under the subcategories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with image and video processing (cs.MM) and the optimization of neural networks (cs.NE).
